<item>
            <title>[PIG-3168] TestMultiQueryBasic.testMultiQueryWithSplitInMapAndMultiMerge fails in trunk</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3168</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2994&quot; title=&quot;Grunt shortcuts&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2994&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2994&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; made explain with no alias be equivalent to explain on the previous alias. This breaks TestMultiQueryBasic.testMultiQueryWithSplitInMapAndMultiMerge because the previous alias is an auto-generated alias not a user-defined alias.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following fixes the test:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
         &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;I = GROUP F2 BY (f7, f8);&quot;&lt;/span&gt; +
         &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;STORE I into &apos;foo4&apos;  using BinStorage();&quot;&lt;/span&gt; +
-        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;explain;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
+        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;explain I;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
